'''伊斯兰国国旗'''又称'''[[黑旗_(伊斯兰教)|黑旗]]'''（{{lang-ar|راية السوداء}}，''Rāyat al-sawdā''），是活动于[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]和[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]的、被认为是[[恐怖组织|恐怖组织]]的军事组织[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]使用的旗帜，近期因该组织的扩张行动而为人所知。旗帜为黑色，上加白色[[清真言|清真言]]，中央为[[穆罕默德之印|穆罕默德之印]]的部分：
: {{lang|ar|{{big|لَا إِلٰهَ إِلَّا الله }}}}
: ''{{transl|ar|DIN|lā ʾilāha ʾillā-llāh}}''
: “万物非主，唯有真主”<ref>N Mohammad (1985), The doctrine of jihad: An introduction, Journal of Law and Religion, 3(2): 381-397</ref>

旗帜中央为白色穆罕默德之印：
: {{lang|ar|{{big|الله رسول محمد}}}}
: ''{{transl|ar|DIN|Allāhu-rasūlu mohamad}}''
: “安拉的使者，穆罕默德”

== 禁止展示 ==
2014年8月起，在[[英國|英國]]<ref>{{Cite news|title=Cameron warns of IS threat to UK|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-28823281|newspaper=BBC News|date=2014-08-17|accessdate=2020-08-21|language=en-GB|archivedate=2019-08-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190830075536/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-28823281|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Terrorism Act 2000|url=http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2000/11/section/13|accessdate=2017-11-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107230643/http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/2000/11/section/13|archivedate=2017-11-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>及[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Dutch ban display of Isis flag in advance Amsterdam march|url=https://www.irishtimes.com/news/world/europe/dutch-ban-display-of-isis-flag-in-advance-amsterdam-march-1.1885354|accessdate=2020-08-21|last=Cluskey|first=Peter|work=The Irish Times|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915113433/https://www.irishtimes.com/news/world/europe/dutch-ban-display-of-isis-flag-in-advance-amsterdam-march-1.1885354|archivedate=2017-09-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>展示伊斯蘭國旗幟將觸犯法律。

2014年9月起，在德國展示伊斯蘭國旗幟列入違反[[德国刑法第86条第一款|德國刑法86a]]條之列，該法專門處理[[納粹主義|納粹]]有關標誌<ref>{{Cite news|title=Germany Bans Support for ISIS|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/09/13/world/europe/germany-bans-support-of-isis.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2014-09-12|accessdate=2020-08-21|issn=0362-4331|language=en-US|first=Melissa|last=Eddy|archivedate=2020-05-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200515222253/https://www.nytimes.com/2014/09/13/world/europe/germany-bans-support-of-isis.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。鄰國[[奧地利|奧地利]]也在同月跟進。<ref>{{cite news|title=Austria bans Isis terror symbols|url=http://www.thelocal.at/20140912/austria-bans-isis-terror-symbols|accessdate=19 November 2014|work=The Local|date=12 September 2014|archivedate=2017-11-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171123091352/https://www.thelocal.at/20140912/austria-bans-isis-terror-symbols|dead-url=no}}</ref>

